{"tid":2054601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台媒指台灣將設港人政治庇護處所 周四公布詳情","createTime":"2020-06-07T09:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T03:04:47.000Z","uid":21470,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"21850b7165d28f98fea027594b028bdea8b57a61","tid":2054601,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:38:53.000Z","msg":"台媒指台灣將設港人庇護處所 周四公布詳情<br />\n07.06.2020 17:04<br />\n<br />\n台灣傳媒報道，總統蔡英文指示訂立的「香港人道救援行動方案」，已經由陸委會根據《港澳條例》草擬好，並送交行政院，星期四通過後，就會對外公布。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，根據方案，台灣當局受理港人申請政治庇護的申請後，會先由安全部門核查身份，並會在獲准居留前，提供基本安置及照顧。當局將來會設置「集中安置處所」，安置在當地無法自行租屋的人。政府亦會編列預算，為尋求庇護的申請人，提供慰問金、安置費及關懷金等，直至獲得居留權。在獲准居留後，當局會提供就學、就業及職業訓練等輔導。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1302410&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1302410%26csid%3D261_341&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=da53d138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1302410&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"a9c04a7b487ecedab7bbf799ea0135073c916d12","tid":2054601,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:42:44.000Z","msg":"台灣真係幫好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfd58df478c3c14220ec00092516dab0ff6a9f7","tid":2054601,"uid":24339,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:47:24.000Z","msg":"有咩事都唔會走，冇可能揼低家人走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10b4282378474439f472767b89abb9b050668ea","tid":2054601,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"